<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="genius-n">genius <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'dʒiːniəs/    美 /'dʒiːniəs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>[常用单数] 天才；天赋：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>has a genius for</strong> languages.
她有语言的天赋。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>天才人物</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Einstein was not only a genius; he was a courageous and kind figure loved by many people.
爱因斯坦不仅是个天才，他还是一个勇敢、善良的人，受到许多人的爱戴。</p><footer>人教新选必① – 1</footer></div></div>